thread.title: Nick C

author: Nick C
title: Nick C
text:
Servcorp William Street have supported my Legal Practise since May 2011. They make my life easier and allow me to focus on my business. It is convenient and easy, I don’t need to worry about operations, maintaining the office or managing a team, Katie and the team do it for me!
The Flexible agreements mean I don’t need to lock into anything long term.
I also like the community culture and have connected with other tenants on the floor, we often work collaboratively which assists us to offer additional services under our respective brands.
The team are professional, friendly and supportive, and the views…. The best in Melbourne!!!
